      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* John Nardone, director for media and research services at Modem Media, Westport, Conn., a unit of True North Communications, was named to the additional duties of managing director at Modem Media New York, formerly named Northern Lights Interactive. He succeeds John Adams, who resigned. Also, Sean Connolly, managing director at Northern Lights Interactive, Hong Kong, becomes managing director of the renamed Modem Media Hong Kong.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>* John Nardone, director for media and research services at Modem Media, Westport, Conn., a unit of True North Communications, was named to the additional duties of managing director at Modem Media New York, formerly named Northern Lights Interactive. He succeeds John Adams, who resigned. Also, Sean Connolly, managing director at Northern Lights Interactive, Hong Kong, becomes managing director of the renamed Modem Media Hong Kong.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
